<item>
            <title>[LU-7877] Suspect locking cleanup in mdt_reint_rename_internal()</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7877</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In mdt_reint_rename_internal():&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
                rc = mdt_reint_object_lock(info, mold, lh_oldp, lock_ibits,
                                           cos_incompat);
                &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (rc != 0)
                        GOTO(out_unlock_old, rc);
...
                rc = mdt_reint_object_lock(info, mold, lh_oldp, lock_ibits,
                                           cos_incompat);
                &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (rc != 0)
                        GOTO(out_unlock_old, rc);
...
out_unlock_old:
        mdt_object_unlock(info, mold, lh_oldp, rc);
out_put_new:
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (mnew != NULL)
                mdt_object_put(info-&amp;gt;mti_env, mnew);
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I guess both of those GOTOs should go to out_put_new?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
